TEXT.Text:
{C=0xFFFF5917/}[Master Chocolatier's House]{C=0xFFFFFFFF/}
It is well known that the taste of the chocolate created by the Master Chocolatier is affected by his mood. Recently the Master Chocolatier has been suffering because of the Love Haters!
Let's help the {C=0xFF00FFFF/}Master Chocolatier{C=0xFFFFFFFF/} defeat the  {C=0xFFFF0000/}Love Haters{C=0xFFFFFFFF/}.
